-- Douglas’s Thalia to Shut 15 Stores to Cut Costs, Abendblatt Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-03-15T17:20:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/douglas-s-thalia-to-shut-15-stores-to-cut-costs-abendblatt-says.html
Douglas Holding AG (DOU) ’s Thalia book-
selling unit plans to close about 15 of its more than 300
outlets because of competition from  Amazon.com Inc. (AMZN) ,  Hamburger
Abendblatt  reported, citing a letter to employees.  The plan may have consequences for personnel, the newspaper
cited an unidentified spokeswoman as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
